This status map provides imagery acquisition status, imagery inspection status, NAIP planned coverage for the year, band type, contractors acquiring the imagery, camera types, and flight seasons. Attribute information for individual layers in the map can be accessed by turning the layer on and clicking on the map.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>farming</dcat:keyword>
